{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01QoNxQ96xKSonDYndo2umnL","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. I need to:\n\n1. Add player profile methods to the `Db` interface\n2. Add a `normalizePlayerProfile` helper\n3. Add implementations in the `createDb` function\n\nLet me also check what `randomBytes` from `crypto` would be available since I need a fallback username generation.\n\nThe spec requires:\n1. `createPlayerProfile(wallet: string): Promise<PlayerProfile>` — calls `generateUserId()` + `generateUsername()`, inserts row, on UNIQUE violation of username retries up to 5 times with new username, if all retries fail uses fallback `user-{random8}`. Returns the created profile.\n\n\n2. `getProfileByWallet(wallet: string): Promise<PlayerProfile | null>` — simple wallet lookup.\n3. `getProfileByIdentifier(identifier: string): Promise<PlayerProfile | null>` — checks if identifier is a user ID (starts with `usr_`) and queries accordingly, otherwise does case-insensitive username lookup.\n4. `updateUsername(wallet: string, newUsername: string): Promise<PlayerProfile>` — enforces a 30-day cooldown from the last username change (first edit is always free), updates both the username and timestamp, and throws if the new username violates the UNIQUE constraint.\n\nNow I need to add these four methods to the `Db` interface, create a `normalizePlayerProfile` helper function, and implement them in the `createDb` return object. For the fallback username generation, I see that `generateUserId()` already creates the `usr_` prefixed IDs, so I'll follow the same pattern with `randomBytes` to generate the `user-{random8}` fallback username. Now I'm handling the unique constraint violations that postgres.js throws with error code '23505', and I need to structure the interface additions, the profile normalization helper, and then the actual implementations before the transaction wrapper.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1319,"cache_read_input_tokens":49581,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1319},"output_tokens":12,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4603cf5e-2eec-42a2-ba7b-9521091bfde1","uuid":"87eeb8b4-65e7-42d3-81ad-02bb1d767244"}
